_054"}, {"decision": "The LMCA had a 60% distal stenosis.  The mid LAD as well as D1 each had 60% stenoses.  The LCX had mild luminal irregularities.  The OM1 branch had a 60% stenosis.  ", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "5952", "end_offset": "6117", "annotation_id": "CU_055"}, {"decision": "The RCA was totally occluded proximally and received collaterals from the LAD as well as right to right collaterals.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "6117", "end_offset": "6233", "annotation_id": "CU_056"}, {"decision": "Hemodynamic evaluation revealed markedly elevated right-sided pressures (mean RA was 22 and RVEDP was 23 mmHg), markedly elevated left-sided pressures (mean PCW was 31 and LVEDP was 32 mmHg), and moderately elevated pulmonary pressures (PA was 51/35 mmHg).", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "6238", "end_offset": "6494", "annotation_id": "CU_057"}, {"decision": "The cardiac index was low-normal at 2.4 L/min/m2 (using an assumed oxygen consumption index).  ", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "6495", "end_offset": "6590", "annotation_id": "CU_058"}, {"decision": "There was no gradient across the aortic valve on pullback of the angled pigtail catheter from the left ventricle to the ascending aorta.  ", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "6590", "end_offset": "6728", "annotation_id": "CU_059"}, {"decision": "The central aortic pressure was supported with both dopamine and subsequently norepinephrine.", "category": "Category 5: Drug related", "start_offset": "6728", "end_offset": "6821", "annotation_id": "CU_060"}, {"decision": "Left ventriculography (using 36 cc of contrast injected at 12cc/sec) revealed a severely reduced ejection fraction of 18%.  There was global hypokinesis and minimal mitral regurgitation.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "6826", "end_offset": "7012", "annotation_id": "CU_061"}, {"decision": "The right heart catheterization was complicated by atrial fibrillation.  The atrial fibrillation was cardioverted with 200J of biphasic current.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "7017", "end_offset": "7161", "annotation_id": "CU_062"}, {"decision": "Three vessel coronary artery disease", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7183", "end_offset": "7219", "annotation_id": "CU_063"}, {"decision": "Severe systolic and diastolic ventricular dysfunction", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7224", "end_offset": "7277", "annotation_id": "CU_064"}, {"decision": "Moderate pulmonary hypertension", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7282", "end_offset": "7313", "annotation_id": "CU_065"}, {"decision": "h/o severe CAD, CHF, DM, htn, hyperlipidemia who p/w acute exacerbation of CHF requiring intubation in the setting of PNA/URI.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7364", "end_offset": "7490", "annotation_id": "CU_066"}, {"decision": "3 vessel disease ", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7534", "end_offset": "7551", "annotation_id": "CU_067"}, {"decision": "severe but no interval progression in 8 years", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7554", "end_offset": "7599", "annotation_id": "CU_068"}, {"decision": "s/p cath [**1-11**] w/o intervention", "category": "Category 6: Therapeutic procedure related", "start_offset": "7601", "end_offset": "7637", "annotation_id": "CU_069"}, {"decision": "As there was no change in CAD, it was felt to CHF was most likely d/t PNA or viral infection.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7639", "end_offset": "7732", "annotation_id": "CU_070"}, {"decision": "The pt was felt to not currently be a candidate for intervention.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "7733", "